com.sun.mirror.apt

Interface RoundState

  • Deprecated. 
    All components of this API have been superseded by the standardized annotation processing API. The replacement for the functionality of this interface is RoundEnvironment.

    @Deprecated
public interface RoundState
    Represents the status of a completed round of annotation processing.
    Since:
    1.5

      Deprecated.
